title: Thanksgiving 2020 Recap, Lamar Jackson COVID news

description:
Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal recap the two thanksgiving games starting with Washington at Dallas (2:00) and then Deshaun Watson and the Texans rolling over Detroit (8:30). The Ravens have some more Covid news involving Lamar Jackson (12:30).
